int Mpu6050::read ( int  start,
uint8_t *  buffer,
int  size 
) [private]

read is a common function to read multiple bytes from an I2C device.

Parameters:
start 
buffer 
size 
Returns:

It uses the boolean parameter for Wire.endTransMission() to be able to hold or release the I2C-bus. This is implemented in Arduino 1.0.1. Only this function is used to read. There is no function for a single byte.
